<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5041889">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5041889/" class="title-link">我们都在写的字。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5041889"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/52615985/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u52615985-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52615985/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">秦小瑾。</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-07-28"
      class="main-meta">2011-07-28 19:14:37</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5041889_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  你问一个学生，一个字为什么这么写，他十有八九是不知道的。就算知道，大概若它能说出一个“象形”“形声”云云。但如若深究，若非专业人士，他就不能说得明白了。在如今这个拼命学习，掌握所谓“英文语法”，大肆宣传“英语构词”“英语起源”的外文崇拜时代，多少人愿意坐下...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5041889/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5041889_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5041889_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










