            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33083617">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">古文和小篆的“王”字都引成了古文的字形，小篆“王”的字形见《说文》</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-10-09 14:18</span>
                  
                </p>
